    ],
    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes </strong>(skins on) into chips</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pigs-in-blankets-bao-with-brussels-sprout-hot-sauce/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pigs-in-blankets-bao-with-brussels-sprout-hot-sauce/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pigs in blankets </strong>to a separate <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-18 mins or until cooked through</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pigs-in-blankets-bao-with-brussels-sprout-hot-sauce/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Trim the ends from your <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong>, then finely slice</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pigs-in-blankets-bao-with-brussels-sprout-hot-sauce/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced sprouts </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pigs-in-blankets-bao-with-brussels-sprout-hot-sauce/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>grated carrot </strong>and <strong>most</strong> of your <strong>chopped chives </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>Brussels Sprout & carrot slaw</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pigs-in-blankets-bao-with-brussels-sprout-hot-sauce/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Pierce your <strong>bao bun packet[s]</strong> with a few holes and <strong>microwave</strong> for 1-2 min</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pigs-in-blankets-bao-with-brussels-sprout-hot-sauce/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>To build your buns, fill each <strong>bao bun</strong> with some of the <strong>Brussels Sprout & carrot slaw</strong>, the <strong>cooked pigs in blankets</strong>, top with your <strong>Brussels Sprout buffalo sauce </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and the <strong>remaining chopped chives </strong>\u2013 these are your <strong>pigs in blanket bao buns</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>pigs in blanket bao buns </strong>with the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>remaining Brussels Sprout & carrot slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
